          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl p-3 mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Safe, Structured Environment</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Professional staff, clear guidelines, and peer support create the foundation for sustainable recovery.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
