          the support and structure you need at every step of your journey.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Standard Program -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 group">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 rounded-2xl w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
